    "Reconstructed expression and histology are considered as cell state-specific expression and histology.",
    "Integration of multiple samples.",
    "To effectively integrate multiple samples, Starfysh initially identifies anchors in each sample by combining spots enriched for cell types and archetypal communities.",
    "The gene markers for each sample are then updated based on the newly defined anchors.",
    "Subsequently, we aggregate the gene markers for each cell type across all samples."
